                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2921" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0433</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9691 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郸酒的移动互联营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Mobile Internet Marketing of Danjiu Liquor</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">庄贵军，林枫</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">邯郸永不分梨酒业销售有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">移动互联网；微信；O2O；网络营销；营销战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Mobile Internet; WeChat; O2O; Internet Marketing; Marketing Strategy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">手机通过与互联网嫁接，成为功能强大的移动互联网。然而，大多数传统企业对如何利用移动互联工具从事营销活动却知之甚少。本案例描述了和君咨询合伙人陆林风先生带领项目组，利用微信这一移动互联工具为永不分梨酒业公司销售郸酒的过程。陆林风先生深入探索白酒的移动互联营销，专门为白酒创立了“新媒体策略 + 双社区模式 + 超级品牌&amp;产品”三大模块构成的“互联网营销1.5 模式”。案例展现了这一模式是如何将移动互联网的特点融入白酒的营销之中，使白酒的移动互联营销成为植根于移动互联网环境的一个完整体系。本案例重在应用营销理论对郸酒的移动互联营销进行分析和解释，一方面帮助学生理解营销学的基本概念和逻辑，引发学生对顾客价值、营销战略和移动互联环境下的营销战略等内容进行深入思考，另一方面对于现有营销理论难以解释的现象，启发学生进行理论创新，提出合理的解释。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Grafting with the internet, mobile phone becomes a powerful mobile internet. However, most firms in traditional industries know little about how to use the tools based on mobile internet in marketing. This case describes a marketing process of Danjiu, an alcohol liquor, by using WeChat. The program team was led by Mr. Lu Linfeng, a partner of Hejun Consulting Limited Company. Mr. Lu actively explored the mobile internet marketing of alcohol liquor, and proposed an “Enterprise’s Internet 1.5 Mode”, composed of “New Media Strategy + Dual-Community Mode + Super Brand &amp; Product” and specialized for mobile internet marketing of alcohol liquor. The case shows how this model integrated the characteristics of mobile internet into marketing of alcohol liquor so as to run as a system. The case discussion will induce students to think more deeply about the contents of customer value, marketing strategy and marketing strategy in mobile internet environment.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《营销管理》、《网络营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">顾客价值、营销战略和移动互联环境下营销战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
